doctor.name: Dr. S.M. Jalal Uddin
doctor.info: Dr. S.M. Jalal Uddin is a Anesthesiologist in Barisal. His qualification is MBBS, DA. He is the Owner, Anesthesiology of  at Shafait General Hospital & ICU, Barisal. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Shafait General Hospital & ICU, Barisal. Practicing hour of Dr. S.M. Jalal Uddin at Shafait General Hospital & ICU, Barisal is 9am to 9pm (Closed: Friday).
